03:01.848 --> 03:04.180
I want malaria.

03:04.317 --> 03:06.251
I'll buy you a mosquito.

03:06.386 --> 03:07.717
All right, now...
now, sit down, please.

03:07.854 --> 03:10.186
I want to... I want to do
my speech for you, okay?

03:10.323 --> 03:13.054
Now, first thing that will
happen is: I'll be introduced.

03:13.193 --> 03:14.126
