framed enough this week.

22:04.156 --> 22:05.646
(doorbell rings)

22:05.791 --> 22:07.725
I'll get it.

22:08.861 --> 22:09.794
All right, everybody.

22:09.929 --> 22:10.987
Hold onto your hats.

22:11.130 --> 22:12.359
