to make.

22:12.498 --> 22:13.431
Richie won.

22:13.566 --> 22:14.692
I couldn't wait, Malph.

22:14.834 --> 22:17.201
- I won?
-(others exclaiming)

22:17.336 --> 22:19.464
- I won.
- I knew it!

22:19.605 --> 22:20.970
Rich, it wasn't even close.

22:21.106 --> 22:21.971
Congratulations.

22:22.107 --> 22:23.370
All right, well, you see that?

22:23.509 --> 22:25.739
The sophomore class
is interested in vital issues.

22:25.878 --> 22:28.176
Yeah, yeah, they want
massage parlors on campus.

22:30.015 --> 22:31.073
You mean I... I won

22:31.217 --> 22:32.582
because I was dressed
in a sheet?

22:32.718 --> 22:35.653
Oh, my brother a sex object.

22:35.788 --> 22:38.052
What difference
does it make how you won?

22:38.190 --> 22:41.057
Now you can make the student
government a better one.

22:41.193 --> 22:43.025
That's the important thing,
Richard.

22:43.162 --> 22:46.063
Hey, congrats, Mr. Prez.

22:46.198 --> 22:48.292
- Mr. Prez?
- FONZIE: That's right.

22:48.434 --> 22:50.562
- I won.
- HOWARD: Mm-hmm.

22:50.703 --> 22:51.727
"Morning, Mr. President."

22:51.871 --> 22:53.032
