22:59.044 --> 23:00.136
HOWARD:
Richard!

23:00.279 --> 23:02.748
Thank you. Thanks very much.

23:02.882 --> 23:05.010
Oh. Yeah.

23:05.150 --> 23:06.982
The president cordially
invites you

23:07.119 --> 23:10.578
to, uh, go to Arnold's with him
and have sodas.

23:10.723 --> 23:13.249
