23:34.413 --> 23:35.608
<i>RICHIE:
All right.</i>

23:35.748 --> 23:37.512
Good. I'll give you
Baltic for Boardwalk.

23:37.650 --> 23:40.415
- No, no, uh-uh.
- Come on, Richard.

23:40.552 --> 23:41.576
I'll tell you one thing,

23:41.720 --> 23:43.154
